venient Python interface is\nprovided. We give a detailed description of MSE and illustrate how to use the\ncode in practice. We demonstrate its operation in a number of examples.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Nov 2020 15:47:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 29 Jan 2021 16:32:44 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 18 Feb 2021 15:08:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-19"}
